{
  "stem": "15578.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because later on-- right the second day, you knew when we arrived that this is crematoriums, and people are getting gassed there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And like when we were there already, people later on did come from Lodz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some people, they right away went into the gas and the children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they children, a lot of children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came from Wilno.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember a lot of-- a lot of children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To see them?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, you could see them from one barrack to the other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can see them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could walk there too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because it was lengthwise, and the barracks was-- they were standing like this, like this, like this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you could go there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sure, that was-- it was open.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean that everybody could see it from far away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only thing, I, I know like, like we went into the shower, yeah?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was a real shower.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- what I've been told in the-- in the crematoriums-- maybe it was even the same what I went in, the shower, that they threw it in the gas through the roof.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we were people who did arrive from Blizyn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They never got gassed, none of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe later on, somebody got sick, and they took us to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Till November.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'44.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That was in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from Birkenau, we went for a very short period of time to Oranienburg and Sachsenhausen, maybe two weeks altogether.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Sachsenhausen?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Oranienburg.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were there I think a few days, a week.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Sachsenhausen also so the same time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from Sachsenhausen, we were transport already to Ohrdruf in very good train, in a train, a passenger train.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
